{"tid":195823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙胞胎姊妹嫁雙胞胎兄弟 還同時懷第二胎","createTime":"2017-04-11T01:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T13:25:32.000Z","uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d394a5e049189e2d4703d3d28b15137c9634ca1","tid":195823,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phprx9zoA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phprx9zoA.jpg&h=935b5846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phphirUT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phphirUT6.jpg&h=cb703959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpdHfSzf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpdHfSzf.jpg&h=de7a7acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哈薩克有對雙胞胎姊妹嫁給了一對雙胞胎兄弟，她們穿一樣的婚紗在同一天舉行婚禮，住在同一棟房子裡，最近甚至同時懷上第二胎，而兄弟倆都是實習獸醫，姊妹倆則都是在學習當老師，根本是巧上加巧！<br />\n當時其中一對先遇見，男方在商店搭訕了女方，兩人相談甚歡，男方就開玩笑問女方說，有沒有個雙胞胎姊妹，來配他的雙胞胎兄弟？豈料還真的有，也就促成了這段姻緣。<br />\n目前他們住在一間三房的公寓內，而結婚後，一對夫婦生下了兒子，另一對生下了女兒，如今姊妹倆又同時懷上第二胎，不少網友猜測，她們是否會生下一對雙胞胎！"},{"pid":"9339ea1b760e02e6da8bf4ea2ce088873a6e3302","tid":195823,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"打亂種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個叫邊個老豆都分唔出"},{"pid":"14c2844c09c078111b8cb3f80407bff1a0d76259","tid":195823,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:34:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4P之<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHappyEnding！！！！<img src=\"/as